title: Federal Court (Repeal) Act, 2014
description: Official consolidated text of Federal Court (Repeal) Act, 2014 (II of 2014) published by The Pakistan Code (General Laws).

provisions.title: Section 1. Short title and commencement
provisions.content:
(1) This Act may be called the Federal
Court(Repeal) Act, 2014.
(2)    It shall come into force at once.

provisions.title: Section 2. Repeal of Act XXV of 1937
provisions.content:
The Federal Court Act, 1937 (XXV of 1937), is hereby
repealed.
